reviewText: Beautiful story - enjoyed  all of Bae Yong-Jun's acting endeavers - would love to see more.

he came from poverty and wanted to better himself by going to college during the day and working full time at night. he fell in love with his beautiful teacher who was just a few years older than him . He wanted to marry her but her parents were dead set against it because he was an orphan and poor.  this is  a sad love story and it is a must see.
